item.description:
It is said, &ldquo;In life, you should plant a tree, father a child, and write a book.&rdquo; Well, two down &hellip; and today&hellip;
&hellip;I rope in the third with the release of the book Mastering Microsoft 365 and SharePoint Online. https://lnkd.in/dvKpWXxt Oorah!
Huge thanks to the wifey, my kids, and my father for their unwavering support&hellip; and patience 🤠, and to everyone who, in any way, inspired making this a reality: this one’s for y&rsquo;all!
